Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.converters

A registry of converters.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Converter<S>
    Able to convert values of a source type to one or more target types.
    ConverterRegistry
    A registry for converters.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassBasedConverter<S,T>
    Abstract superclass for all converters that are able to convert from a single source type into a single target type, both of which are classes.
    DefaultConverterRegistry
    A default converter registry implementation.

Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.converters Description

A registry of converters. The wiki contains more information on conversion.
